# Read anonymized data

```{r}
f <- file.path("C:/Users/chanb/Box Sync/PrintValveGroup AnonymyzedData",
               "BenPrintValveDataSet.xlsx")
D <-
  read_excel(f, col_names = FALSE, skip = 1, na = "x") %>% 
  filter(!is.na(X2)) %>%
  select(-(4:11)) %>%
  rename(group = X0,
         id = X1,
         casecon = X2,
         # segmentation = X3,
         # ratioSmoothWrap = X4,
         # exportTrimHollow = X5,
         # pointsPlanes = X6,
         # mirror = X7,
         # valveCreated = X8,
         # centroidCalc = X9,
         # allCalcs = X10,
         NR = X11,
         NRfrac = X12,
         RL = X13,
         RLfrac = X14,
         LN = X15,
         LNfrac = X16,
         areaTotalValue = X17,
         areaTotal = X18,
         areaOrifice = X19,
         diameterValve = X20,
         areaValve = X21,
         ratioAreaCoapToDiameterValve = X22,
         ratioAreaCoapToAreaOrifice = X23,
         ratioAreaCoapToAreaValve = X24,
         notesMimics = X25,
         notes3Matic = X26)
```

```{r}
D %>% group_by(casecon) %>% tally %>% kable
summary(D)
```
